# Testing Standards - MoonProject

## 1. Nguyên tắc

- Test **pure logic**, không test MonoBehaviour trực tiếp
- Extract logic ra pure C# class → test class đó (xem `extract_pure_logic.md`)
- Mock dependencies qua interface
- Test phải chạy nhanh (< 1s per test), không cần Unity Play mode

## 2. Cấu trúc Test

```
Assets/
├── Tests/
│   ├── EditMode/
│   │   ├── DreamyHarvest.Tests.EditMode.asmdef
│   │   ├── Gameplay/
│   │   │   ├── FarmLogicTests.cs
│   │   │   ├── AnimalLogicTests.cs
│   │   │   └── EconomyTests.cs
│   │   ├── Data/
│   │   │   ├── DataMigrationTests.cs
│   │   │   └── SerializationTests.cs
│   │   └── Mocks/
│   │       ├── MockConfigProvider.cs
│   │       └── MockDataProvider.cs
│   └── PlayMode/
│       ├── DreamyHarvest.Tests.PlayMode.asmdef
│       └── Integration/
│           ├── ManagerContainerTests.cs
│           └── SaveLoadTests.cs
```

## 3. Naming Convention

```csharp
[Test]
public void {Method}_{Scenario}_{ExpectedResult}()

// Ví dụ:
public void TryPlant_WhenNotEnoughCoins_ReturnsNotEnoughCoins()
public void CanHarvest_WhenTimeElapsed_ReturnsTrue()
public void AddItem_WhenItemExists_IncreasesCount()
```

## 4. Mock Patterns

### Mock cho services hiện tại
```csharp
public interface ITimeProvider
{
    long GetCurrentTimestamp();
}

public class MockTimeProvider : ITimeProvider
{
    public long MockTime { get; set; }
    public long GetCurrentTimestamp() => MockTime;
}
```

### Sử dụng trong test
```csharp
[TestFixture]
public class FarmLogicTests
{
    private FarmLogic _logic;
    private FarmState _state;
    private MockTimeProvider _time;

    [SetUp]
    public void SetUp()
    {
        _state = new FarmState();
        _time = new MockTimeProvider { MockTime = 1000 };
        var config = CreateTestPlantConfig("wheat", cost: 10, harvestTime: 300);
        _logic = new FarmLogic(_state, config, _time);
    }

    [Test]
    public void TryPlant_WhenHasEnoughCoins_PlantSuccessfully()
    {
        var result = _logic.TryPlant("wheat", currentCoins: 100);

        Assert.AreEqual(PlantResult.Success, result);
        Assert.AreEqual("wheat", _state.plantId);
        Assert.AreEqual(1000, _state.timeStampPlant);
    }

    [Test]
    public void CanHarvest_BeforeHarvestTime_ReturnsFalse()
    {
        _logic.TryPlant("wheat", currentCoins: 100);
        _time.MockTime = 1200; // 200s < 300s harvestTime

        Assert.IsFalse(_logic.CanHarvest());
    }

    [Test]
    public void CanHarvest_AfterHarvestTime_ReturnsTrue()
    {
        _logic.TryPlant("wheat", currentCoins: 100);
        _time.MockTime = 1500; // 500s > 300s harvestTime

        Assert.IsTrue(_logic.CanHarvest());
    }
}
```

## 5. Những gì BẮT BUỘC test

| Module | Cần test | Lý do |
|--------|----------|-------|
| Economy (Coin/Gem/Energy) | Add/Remove/Check balance | Ảnh hưởng IAP, player progression |
| Farm/Animal growth timing | Plant → Grow → Harvest cycle | Core gameplay |
| Order matching | Order requirements vs inventory | Player rewards |
| Data migration | Old format → new format | Mất data = mất player |
| Leaderboard scoring | Score calculation, ranking | Competition fairness |

## 6. Những gì KHÔNG CẦN test

- UI display logic (set text, set sprite)
- MonoBehaviour lifecycle glue code
- Inspector-configured ScriptableObject
- Third-party SDK wrappers

---

### Ví dụ ĐÚNG

```csharp
[Test]
public void RemoveItem_WhenExactAmount_RemovesFromInventory()
{
    var inventory = new List<CountObject> { new CountObject("wheat", 5) };
    var logic = new InventoryLogic(inventory);

    bool result = logic.RemoveItem("wheat", 5);

    Assert.IsTrue(result);
    Assert.AreEqual(0, logic.GetItemCount("wheat"));
}
```

### Ví dụ SAI

```csharp
[Test]
public void TestFarm() // Tên không mô tả
{
    var farm = new GameObject().AddComponent<Farm>(); // Test MonoBehaviour trực tiếp
    farm.TryPlanting("wheat"); // Phụ thuộc Unity runtime
    Assert.IsTrue(farm.CanHarvest); // Flaky - phụ thuộc coroutine
}
```
